content:
Standardize Responses with Quick Text

Quick text saves users time and helps you standardize your company messaging. With quick text, you can insert predefined messages like greetings, answers to common questions, and short notes.

REQUIRED EDITIONS

Available in Salesforce Classic: Group, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
Available in Lightning Experience: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To set up quick text, enable it, give users access, and create messages. Users can then insert the messages into conversations and records.

Here are three ways to make the most of quick text:
 Organize messages into shareable folders by business unit or category.
Use categories like greetings, FAQ, closings, or custom categories.
Let selected users create and manage their own quick text messages.
